Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.21,0:00:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这…这家伙什么来头
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.78,0:00:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你没有受伤吧 女士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.31,0:00:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.97,0:00:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,长枪骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.97,0:00:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(640,665)}Knight Lancer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.34,0:02:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这是银光骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.34,0:02:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(673.079,665)}Sliver Lancer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.60,0:02:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是长枪骑士的英雄伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.60,0:02:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(573.843,665)}Knight Lancer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.43,0:02:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,真…真绪你画画真好看呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.97,0:03:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这是阳光骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.97,0:03:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(673.079,665)}Sunny Lancer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.01,0:03:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然还是修行中的英雄 但她非常努力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.77,0:03:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好可爱呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.64,0:03:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不不 画的是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.62,0:03:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.72,0:03:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这个英雄的原型 就是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这是玫瑰骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(673.798,665)}Rose Lancer
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.09,0:04:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,有哪里好笑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.38,0:04:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.06,0:04:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 羽炎劳你费心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.64,0:04:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.23,0:04:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,真绪小姐那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.06,0:04:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,虽说他是来谢罪的 但留下来等还是会很尴尬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.46,0:04:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是让他去接人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.96,0:04:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,叶太郎不在的话 就谈不上谢罪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.24,0:04:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那些家伙是什么人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.44,0:04:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,得快点告诉老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.39,0:04:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,现在可不能让他知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.58,0:04:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,影子剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.58,0:04:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(640,665)}Shadow Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.03,0:05:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,和爸爸一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.49,0:05:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是正义的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.00,0:05:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.07,0:05:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.23,0:05:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.99,0:05:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.48,0:05:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你的师傅也会感到高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.94,0:05:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.33,0:05:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,连你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么啊 德尔恭先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.87,0:05:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 叶太郎什么时候才回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,因为真绪不知道叶太郎就是长枪骑士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(822.652,665)}Knight Lancer
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦 羽炎都去接他了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.05,0:05:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,难为他了 长枪骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.05,0:05:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(711.191,665)}Knight Lancer
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,真绪 他肯定马上就回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.84,0:05:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,叶太郎看到你画的画会很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,也对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.85,0:06:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 叶太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.54,0:06:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,德尔贡先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,叶太郎能快点回来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.61,0:06:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,今天骑士部继续休息哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.28,0:06:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,阳月学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:06:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.01,0:07:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.00,0:07:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,花房君他下落不明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.31,0:07:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.31,0:07:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,真绪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.04,0:07:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.92,0:07:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,麻烦你看下家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.90,0:07:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好像找到线索了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.51,0:07:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.42,0:07:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.51,0:08:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 你最近怎么不来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.72,0:08:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不… 等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.17,0:08:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都很期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.51,0:08:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,朱藤小姐 找到他了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.46,0:08:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,多亏有大家帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.96,0:08:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,依子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.29,0:08:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不会错的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.77,0:08:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,叶太郎他在凤莱岛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.63,0:09:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.69,0:09:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,羽炎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.45,0:09:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你…你干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.47,0:09:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是在泡个澡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.56,0:09:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到还有其他人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.37,0:09:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋 别过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.55,0:09:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.70,0:09:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我问你们 我家的浴池不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.94,0:10:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,馆…馆长？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.32,0:10:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,为…为什么馆长也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.79,0:10:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,羽炎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样 我是最棒的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.41,0:10:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.20,0:10:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.06,0:10:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,就成为我的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.11,0:10:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,成为我的人吧 叶太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.35,0:10:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,爱丽丝 之后事就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.17,0:10:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.64,0:10:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我也…也带上我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.28,0:10:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,依子你们是要去叶太郎那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.67,0:10:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那我也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.89,0:10:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.82,0:11:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能带你去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,依子姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.10,0:11:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,真绪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.17,0:11:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.44,0:11:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,阻碍妈妈的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.38,0:12:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,听好了 不许打架
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.02,0:12:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.19,0:12:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,听话！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.45,0:12:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.10,0:12:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,没啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.85,0:12:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.18,0:12:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.37,0:12:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,让我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,真绪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.81,0:12:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 他的骑士身份要保密
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.45,0:12:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,真绪 你为什么要这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.41,0:12:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.09,0:12:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,就让我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.09,0:12:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.00,0:12:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,想去叶太郎的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.09,0:12:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,真绪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.78,0:13:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我也 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.88,0:13:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想去找他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.47,0:13:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.72,0:13:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,到叶太郎的身边去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.80,0:13:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,真绪…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.37,0:13:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.62,0:13:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,羽花
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.65,0:13:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那个大妈是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.54,0:13:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你不也是被拐来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.08,0:14:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.98,0:14:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说为什么你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.02,0:14:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.17,0:14:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,就是你！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.26,0:14:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么搞的 为什么叶太郎和个大妈都进了浴室？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.26,0:14:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,叶太郎是我疏忽了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.66,0:14:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,但馆长我也没看见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.83,0:14:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,德尔贡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,德尔贡…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,德尔贡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.76,0:14:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,叶太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.66,0:14:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.42,0:14:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.36,0:15:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,温泉玩得开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.40,0:15:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.02,0:15:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你要…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.62,0:15:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,馆长想让你做她的直属骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,因为听说你打赢了金刚寺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.02,0:15:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,老爹才没输！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.03,0:15:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,羽炎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.68,0:15:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.56,0:15:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但这也太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.14,0:16:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好久没呼吸到这里的空气了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.01,0:16:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,看呀 有个女仆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.16,0:16:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,骑士岛上居然还有女仆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.98,0:16:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,的确都说骑士和女仆是一个时代的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.57,0:16:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你们最好先逃命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.13,0:16:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这位女士是人称「鲜血王冠」的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.96,0:16:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,如果惹毛了这种人物的话 你们小命可就难保了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.65,0:16:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,两小子吓得都忘了同伙了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.66,0:16:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,非常抱歉 认不出朱藤小姐骑士身份的人多起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.97,0:16:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不久 吉尔哈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.29,0:17:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,保持克制啊 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.72,0:17:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,万一和四神 和馆长直属的四个骑士之一闹起来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.10,0:17:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,等于就是和整个东亚地区的骑士为敌了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.30,0:17:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,还得要一会才到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.68,0:17:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 羽花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.68,0:17:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.77,0:17:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,全是弟弟妹妹们在努力着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都想救自己的家人 为了救出羽炎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.75,0:17:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.18,0:18:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到依子这么快就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.04,0:18:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,您叫我吗 馆长？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.66,0:18:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,叶太郎还是不肯成为我的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.93,0:18:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.13,0:18:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,馆长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.93,0:18:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这种做法果然还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.96,0:18:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得依子会放弃叶太郎吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.99,0:18:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.38,0:18:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,算了 我自己去解决
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.74,0:18:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,请稍等！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.92,0:18:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,叶太郎自己正混乱着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.75,0:18:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,至少再给他点考虑的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.98,0:19:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,叫吉尔哈好好牵制住她们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.72,0:19:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.41,0:19:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.58,0:19:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,馆长 您就这么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,中意叶太郎吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.21,0:19:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,吉尔哈真慢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.81,0:19:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我和馆长联系过了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.53,0:20:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,她暂时还是回不来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.67,0:20:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,吉尔哈 叶太郎在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.32,0:20:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你找他有什么事情吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.22,0:20:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.88,0:20:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,想把我们关这里多久
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.26,0:20:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.32,0:20:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说就算你道歉也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.09,0:20:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.62,0:20:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,吃饭了 叶太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.67,0:20:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉把你们关在这
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.62,0:20:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你要听那个老太婆的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.57,0:21:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是骑士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.24,0:21:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,却要听那个任性 随意 粗鲁 自我主义的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.90,0:21:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不许说馆长的坏话！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.50,0:21:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,多亏馆长 我这样的人才能当上骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.87,0:21:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,多亏了这个馆长给我的假面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.24,0:21:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我才能战胜弱小的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.25,0:21:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,德尔贡…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.91,0:21:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,至今为止 我也全是靠着假面…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.97,0:21:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 我只是为了隐藏骑士的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.07,0:21:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,羽炎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.33,0:21:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,叶太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.24,0:21:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.05,0:21:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,快去找医生！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.46,0:21:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是我连累你一起遭罪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.43,0:21:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,至少 至少就你一人也…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.68,0:23:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,白姬你的悄声步 脚法一流啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.68,0:23:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.29,0:23:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,安静！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.30,0:23:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,被依子发现 小命就没了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.52,0:24:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,下集的「枪与假面」是潜入作战
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.03,0:24:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们也潜入依子的房间 找出她的把柄
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.60,0:24:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,还 还是算了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.00,0:24:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,会被杀了的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.79,0:24:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两个真是没胆子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.21,0:24:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不入虎穴焉得虎子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.10,0:24:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你们在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.23,0:24:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 爱丽丝和玉凤在密谋潜入您的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.23,0:24:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,当然我是不会这么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.95,0:24:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,白姬！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.26,0:24:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,她背叛了
